1 install node.js
	http://nodejs.org/

2 npm install bower (npm comme with node normally)

Dans portfolio
npm update

cd apps
bower update

cd marionette
bower update

cd react
npm update

//only if you want the react application to debugged
npm start& //launching react mode watch (n)


//launching server
cd portfolio/server
node server.js& 

//go to page 
http://localhost:8000/



